---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import bookCover1 from "assets/cover1.jpg";
import bookCover2 from "assets/cover2.jpg";
---

<main
  class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 place-items-center pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-12 md:pb-24">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1 hidden md:block">
    <Picture
      src={bookCover1}
      alt="Smart Cooking 1"
      widths={[200, 400, 600]}
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 620px"
      loading="eager"
      format="avif"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1 hidden md:block">
    <Picture
      src={bookCover2}
      alt="Smart Cooking 2"
      widths={[200, 400, 600]}
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 620px"
      loading="eager"
      format="avif"
    />
  </div>
  <div>
    <h1
      class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
      Why learn to cook?
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      We are passionate about communicating the fun of cooking and the rewards
      of healthy eating. The objective is to introduce students to a wider range
      of cooking and to develop their experience and appreciation of classic
      dishes. Students gain a sense of achievement and confidence by learning in
      a stimulated and fun environment. They also learn personal, time
      management skills and organisational skills They take responsibility and
      learn to be organised. They also make new friends. To book a place a
      (deposit â‚¬50) required
    </p>
  </div>
</main>
